# V2.x bootstrap-skill · profile atom singleton dir
#
# At runtime this directory holds exactly one file:
#   atom_profile_main.json  (singleton, D-010)
#
# The file is created by:
#   - atomsyn-cli bootstrap --commit (trigger=bootstrap_initial)
#   - GUI calibration POST /atoms/atom_profile_main/calibrate-profile
#     (trigger=user_calibration)
#
# Both routes go through scripts/lib/evolution.mjs::applyProfileEvolution
# which enforces the singleton + previous_versions[] invariants.
#
# This .gitkeep keeps the directory present in fresh clones / new installs
# so seeding the data dir does not have to mkdir on first profile write.
